data.title: House prices for Atlas Mill, Bentinck Street, Bolton, BL1
data.meta_description: Detailed, accurate and up to date house prices & rental prices for Bentinck Street, Bolton, BL1.
data.text:
The recent census recorded whether a resident owned or rented their home.

In the area around Atlas Mill, Bentinck Street, Bolton, BL1 , 47.3 % of property is privately rented and 22.0 % is privately owned with a mortgage .

The graph below shows how this compares to Greater London and the rest of England & Wales.

The recent census recorded the highest level of education achieved by residents in the local area.

In the area around Atlas Mill, Bentinck Street, Bolton, BL1 , 19.3 % of residents are recorded as possessing school level qualifications and 27.7 % as possessing degree level qualifications.
